      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you\u2019re heading out on a road trip or just cruising around town, it handles beautifully! It\u2019s well-loved and totally ready for its next owner to jump in and start making memories. Come take it for a spin!",
