    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I'm parting with my car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants quality without the brand-new price tag. It's clean, dependable, and ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
