    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS for optimal volumetric efficiency across the rev range. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring exceptional traction out of corners. The chassis remains composed with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, maintaining the sharp handling characteristics of the original MacPherson strut/multi-link suspension geometry. Mechanically sound with documented valve clearances and a healthy cooling system, this M3 offers a pure, analog driving experience.",
